# This setting add most usefull flags for audio work and proaudio.
# We don't want pulse audio to mess with a proaudio setup, but as it can
# be disabled when installed, we put that flag here in order to let
# the user possibility to change it easily.
USE="audiofile cddb cdparanoia dssi ffmpeg fftw fluidsynth jack jackmidi ladspa lame lash libsamplerate lv2 midi mikmod mms modplug musepack -pulseaudio osc raw sndfile taglib theora timidity twolame vcd wav wavpack"
